 among them on that day?\u201d The Prophet\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":19479,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/07\/13\/supplication-dua-for-calamity\/","url_meta":{"origin":17935,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Dua: To Allah we belong, to Allah we will return","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 13, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Umm Salamah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cNo Muslim is afflicted with a calamity but that he should say what Allah has commanded him: Indeed, to Allah we belong and to Allah we will return. (2:156) O Allah, reward me in my affliction\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":22505,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2016\/04\/09\/muslims-nafs-wahid\/","url_meta":{"origin":17935,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Brotherhood: Believers are a community like one soul","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 9, 2016","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Nu\u2019man ibn Bashir reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe Muslims are like a single man. If the eye is afflicted, the whole body is afflicted. If the head is afflicted, the whole body is afflicted.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 2586 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":40576,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/07\/04\/humma-purifies-sin\/","url_meta":{"origin":17935,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Illness: Do not curse fever as it purifies from sin","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 4, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: Fever was mentioned in front of the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, and a man cursed it. The Prophet said, \u201cDo not curse fever, for it cleanses sins just as fire cleanses iron from impurities.\u201d Source: Sunan Ibn Ma\u0304jah 3469 Grade: Sahih li\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":3150,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/05\/08\/fever-expiates-fire-gold\/","url_meta":{"origin":17935,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Sickness: Fever expiates sins, just as fire purifies gold","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 8, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Umm al-Ala reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, visited me when I was sick, and he said, \u201cBe cheerful, O mother of al-Ala. When a Muslim is sick, Allah takes away his sins just as fire takes away impurities in gold and silver.\u201d Source: Sunan\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","widt